# Compiled binary outputs (we build into bin/ so source tree stays clean)
/bin/

# Go test artifacts
*.test
*.out
coverage.txt

# Release artifacts (cross-compiled binaries from the release workflow)
/dist/

# Lockfile sidecar files (machine-local locking state)
seal.json.lock
seal.json.tmp.*

# Agent / IDE local state at the project root (per-user, not shared).
# Anchored with leading `/` so fixtures under testdata/ aren't swallowed.
/.claude/
/.codex/
/.opencode/
/.idea/
